flowchart LR
    U[User Intent] --> ORCH[Orchestrator]
    ORCH --> CLS[Intent Classifier]
    ORCH --> RET[Retriever]
    RET --> SAN[Context Sanitizer]
    SAN --> LLM[Model]
    LLM --> POL[Intent-to-Tool Policy]
    POL --> APP[Approval Gate]
    APP --> SBX[Sandboxed Tool Runtime]

    AUD[Audit + Provenance Log] --> POL
    AUD --> SBX

    NOTE1[Untrusted retrieval never directly authorizes tools]
    NOTE2[High-risk actions require step-up approval]

    POL -.-> NOTE1
    APP -.-> NOTE2
